<Page x:Class="GraphElementGenerationSYS.Pages.Polygon1"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      Height="480" Width="670"
      Title="Polygon1">

    <FlowDocumentScrollViewer>
        <FlowDocument>
            <FlowDocument.Style>
                <Style TargetType="{x:Type FlowDocument}">
                    <Setter Property="LineHeight" Value="2"/>
                    <Setter Property="PageWidth" Value="670"/>
                    <Setter Property="PagePadding" Value="0 20 10 50"/>
                </Style>
            </FlowDocument.Style>

            <Section Margin="10 10 10 50">
                <Paragraph TextAlignment="Center" FontSize="20">正方形生成法</Paragraph>

                <Paragraph Margin="20" TextAlignment="Center">
                    此算法原理跟矩形生成算法是一致的，详见矩形模块的文档。
                </Paragraph>

            </Section>
        </FlowDocument>
    </FlowDocumentScrollViewer>




</Page>
